STATE EX REL. WARE
v.
MOHR 2018-1013 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 10, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss or in the alternative motion for summary judgment. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

DeWine, J., dissents and would grant an alternative writ.
